  <SourceScript>k__BackingField: "Crystalpher: ...\r\n\r\nCrystalpher: (Hello. Do
    you remember me?)\r\n\r\nCrystalpher: (I suppose I am recognizable from a crowd.)\r\n\r\nCrystalpher:
    (I require a special type of elixir to keep myself moving.)\r\n\r\nCrystalpher:
    (Unfortunately, it is quite expensive in most places.)\r\n\r\nCrystalpher: (And
    its hard to find work when you can\u2019t speak.)\r\n\r\nCrystalpher: (Or you\u2019re
    made of crystals.)\r\n\r\nCrystalpher: (In any case. The elixer is much like
    an ointment.)\n\nCrystalpher: (The ointment relieves chronic pain.)\r\n\r\nCrystalpher:
    (I would greatly appreciate if you could make this for me.)\r\n"
